1.54 line counting p23, this explains my confusion, which is, when there is more than one "=", the sequence of these = is
（赋值结合次序由右向左）（猜测：如果由左向右的话，则每个变量到最后值绝大概率都不一样，nw给nl，nc给nw）from right to left,
for example,nl = nw = nc = 0 equals to nl = (nw = (nc = 0)); 
this one explains how some complex function call is done which i meet 
on the CS61A SITP course, using python for programming.

so, = right to left
operator || means OR
escape sequence \t means tab character
operator && means AND
&& or || left to right
此处，当逻辑运算知道c是一个空格，那么它就不可能是\n或\t，则之后的test其是否为\n或\t就不做了。
另 brace 和 parenthesis, brace指{}，parenthesis指().

